        <h1 style="margin: 0;"><img src="/logo.png" alt="gamePLUS"></h1><a href="/">‚Üê Go back to home page</a><hr>

        <h2 id="what-is">What is gamePLUS?</h2>
        <p>At ninePLUS, we're building a chat app called <a href="https://www.nineplus.sh/quarky">Quarky</a>.<br><a href="https://support.discord.com/hc/en-us/articles/7931156448919-Activity-Status-Recent-Activity">Similarly to Discord</a>, Quarky can display what game you're playing on your profile.</p>
        <p>We needed a way to detect what games are running, and this is that.<br>gamePLUS stores the icon, executables (<code><%= sampleGame.executables[0].name %></code>) and name (<i><%= sampleGame.name %></i>) for games.</p>
        <p>This way, you can see exactly what someone's playing:</p>
        <div class="gaming">
            <p>Playing a game</p>
            <div class="gamewrap">
                <img class="gamelogo" src="/game/<%= sampleGame._id %>/icon">
                <div class="gamedata">
                    <b><%= sampleGame.name %></b>
                    <p>12:34 elapsed</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <p class="gamedisclaim">Game chosen at random from the <a href="/games">full list of games</a>.<br>ninePLUS does not own the rights to <%= sampleGame.name %> &mdash; for demonstrational purposes only.</p>

        <img src="/juice.jpg" style="float: left; margin-right: 2em;" width="255">
        <h2 id="submit-edits" style="margin-top: 0;">Help, help! A game is missing or being detected improperly!</h2>
        <p>You have a few ways to submit changes to gamePLUS, so pick whatever you're the most comfortable with.</p>
        <ul class="your-fates">
            <li><b>RECOMMENDED FOR ADDING:</b> You can suggest games directly in <a href="https://roald.hakase.life">Quarky Desktop</a>.<br>Open the game, then go to your Quarky settings. "Playing status", then "suggest a game".<br>A list of currently running apps will appear, pick the one that looks like the game, then submit. Done!</li>
            <li><b>RECOMMENDED FOR EDITING:</b> gamePLUS game pages (like <a href="/game/<%= sampleGame._id %>">this one</a>) have a support icon in the bottom right.<br>It will fill in the game name and link, so just replace "Describe the issue here..." with your desired change.<br>You can find game pages by using the search box on the <a href="/">home page</a>.</li>
            <li>If you just want to send an e-mail yourself, you can go to <a href="https://www.nineplus.sh/support.html">https://www.nineplus.sh/support.html</a> or e-mail <a href="mailto:support@nineplus.sh">support@nineplus.sh</a>.</li>
